						<summary>

						<p>Like No. 282 above this also records a gift of 2 <hi rend="italic">kāśu</hi> to the temple, by Ādanūr Śrīdharaṉ Śatti-Bhaṭṭaṉ of Śuttavallichchēri in Suttavalli-chaturvēdimaṅgalam on his own behalf and on behalf of his father Tiruveṇkāḍaṉ Śrīdhara-Bhaṭṭa Sarvakratuyājiyār for a lamp and a water-pot.</p>						

